ngineer-information-processing_3/#2-%EB%B0%98%EC%82%AC-%EA%B7%9C%EC%B9%99\">2) 반사 규칙</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/engineer-information-processing_3/#3-%EA%B2%B0%ED%95%A9-%EA%B7%9C%EC%B9%99\">3) 결합 규칙</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/engineer-information-processing_3/#5-%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%84%B0%EB%B2%A0%EC%9D%B4%EC%8A%A4-%ED%9A%8C%EB%B3%B5-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B2%95\">5. 데이터베이스 회복 기법</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/engineer-information-processing_3/#1-%ED%9A%8C%EB%B3%B5recovery%EC%9D%B4%EB%9E%80\">1) 회복(Recovery)이란</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/engineer-information-processing_3/#2-%EC%9E%A5%EC%95%A0%EC%9D%98-%EC%9C%A0%ED%98%95\">2) 장애의 유형</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/engineer-information-processing_3/#3-%ED%9A%8C%EB%B3%B5-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B2%95\">3) 회복 기법</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/engineer-information-processing_3/#3-1-%EC%A6%89%EA%B0%81-%EA%B0%B1%EC%8B%A0-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B2%95-immediate-update\">3-1) 즉각 갱신 기법 (Immediate Update)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/engineer-information-processing_3/#3-2-%EC%97%B0%EC%82%B0-%EA%B0%B1%EC%8B%A0-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B2%95-deffered-update\">3-2) 연산 갱신 기법 (Deffered Update)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/engineer-information-processing_3/#3-3-%EA%B2%80%EC%82%AC%EC%A0%90-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B2%95-check-point\">3-3) 검사점 기법 (Check Point)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/engineer-information-processing_3/#3-4-%EA%B7%B8%EB%A6%BC%EC%9E%90-%ED%8E%98%EC%9D%B4%EC%A7%80-%EB%8C%80%EC%B2%B4-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B2%95-shadow-paging---%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EA%B0%80-%ED%95%84%EC%9A%94-%EC%97%86%EC%9D%8C\">3-4) 그림자 페이지 대체 기법 (Shadow Paging) - 로그가 필요 없음</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/engineer-information-processing_3/#%EC%B0%B8%EC%A1%B0\">(참조)</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/engineer-information-processing_3/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[정보처리기사/필기] 3과목 <데이터베이스 구축> 오답정리","date":"Sep 23, 2020","tags":["CS"],"keywords":["정처기","소프트웨어","데이터베이스","정규화","필기","오답노트"],"update":"Jan 01, 0001"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/engineer-information-processing_3/","series":[{"slug":"/engineer-information-processing_1/",